<h2>APPLY TO SJTU</h2>
<p>Shanghai Jiao Tong University is open to students from all over the world. &#160;It offers a number of English programs and English courses in the areas of engineering, sciences, life sciences, economics, humanities and social sciences. &#160;Among them, &#160;there are 10 undergraduate programs in English, 200 undergraduate courses in English,<span style="background-color: transparent;">&#160;27 graduate &#160;programs in English, and 283 graduate English courses.&#160;</span>
</p>
<p>To enter SJTU&#160; as an international student, you are required to have a passport and valid visa (student visa) issued by overseas missions of the Chinese Government.&#160;</p>
<p>Before entering China, the student must obtain a visa that conforms to the stated purpose. You are required to bring your passport, admission permission to the Chinese Embassy or Consulate to obtain a visa.<br />If you enter China with another type of visa, you should replace it with student visa immediately after you arrive.</p>
 
<h3>How to apply</h3>
<p><strong><span class="font-color-blue"><a target="_blank" title="http://apply.sjtu.edu.cn" href="http://apply.sjtu.edu.cn"><span class="font-color-blue">Apply online</span>
</a>
</span>
</strong>（<strong><span class="font-color-pink">Application system is open now.</span>
</strong>）
</p>
